songs.title: Die With You (Island Version)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Woke up this mornin' from a nightmare
Four in the mornin' with a fear in my eyes
Looked to my left and you were right there
I started cryin' 'cause it made me realize
No one is here, we are alone, babe
We are alone with our love
No one's out there, we are alone, babe
We are alone with our love

[Chorus]
When the world ends
I think I wanna die with you, no, no-no-no (Baby)
When the world ends
I think I wanna die with you, no, no-no-no (Baby)
When the world ends
I think I wanna die with you, no, no-no-no (Baby)
When the world ends
I think I wanna die with you, no, no-no-no (Baby)
When the world ends (By your side)
I think I wanna die with you, no, no-no-no (Baby)
